<view class="page"><view class="topic-intro"><view class="topic-icon">#</view><view><view class="title">创建地点话题</view><view class="muted">发言后话题会永久保留在消息列表</view></view></view><text class="field-label">话题名称</text><input class="input" placeholder="例如：新都桥加油排队情况" value="{{form.name}}" data-key="name" bindinput="input"/><text class="field-label">锚定地点</text><view class="location-field" bindtap="location"><text>{{form.location||'选择地图地点'}}</text><text>选择 ›</text></view><view class="rules"><view class="card-title">话题规则</view><view>· 24小时无新消息会转入历史话题</view><view>· 再次发言可恢复为活跃话题</view><view>· 请勿发布车牌、电话等隐私信息</view></view><button class="primary-btn submit" bindtap="submit">创建并进入话题</button></view>
